  "texts": [
    "This has prompted ongoing investigations into its practical applications across various domains, including education and beyond.",
    "Notably, ChatGPT demonstrates potential in tailoring educational content to offer students a personalized learning experience [10].",
    "Some researchers advocate its capacity to create interactive learning environments that foster engagement and motivation [11], while others highlight its versatility in elaborating on diverse subjects [12].",
    "Several studies underscore its role in enhancing critical skills like critical thinking, problem-solving, and communication [13][14][15].However, certain studies caution against the potential drawbacks of ChatGPT, particularly its seamless access to extensive information, which might impede students' independent critical thinking [16][17][18].",
    "Concerns arise regarding overreliance on AI, potentially hindering the full development of analytical and evaluative skills."
  ],
